/**
 * @brief Returns a random Special Infected
 *
 * @param alive			-1 = Any. 0 = Only dead players. 1 = Only alive players
 * @param bots			-1 = Any. 0 - Only real players. 1 = Only fake players
 *
 * @return Client index or 0 if none
